| `FR_ApplyNotificationDeliveryRules` | Map `event_type` → channels; đọc spec §6 routing table |
| `FR_RespectNotificationSettings` | `(user_id, event_type)` → allow_in_app/push/email |
| `FR_SkipSelfNotification` | So sánh `actor_id` vs recipient |
| `FR_CreateInAppNotification` | Template title/body; `reference_type`, `reference_id`, `metadata` JSONB |

## Handler pattern (khuyến nghị)

```text
NotificationEventHandler (interface)
  ├── supports(eventType): boolean
  └── handle(NotificationEvent event): HandlerResult

ProcessPendingNotificationEventsUseCase
  → resolve handler registry
  → transaction: in-app records + mark event
  → after commit: push/email (tránh long TX)
```

Mỗi `FR_Handle*Notification` / `FR_Send*Email` thường là **một handler** hoặc **email sender strategy** — không một class God-switch 500 dòng.

## Notification-specific Rules

- **Consumer only** — không thêm `outbox_events` publish từ notification-service.
- Title/content từ **template** trong code/config, không copy raw từ producer.
- Fan-out announcement: batch insert, idempotent per `(announcement_id, user_id)` — xem `FR_FanOutSystemAnnouncement`.
- `SYSTEM_ANNOUNCEMENT_SENT` / `SYSTEM_ANNOUNCEMENT_PUBLISHED` — chấp nhận alias.
- Commerce events: map `COMMERCE_PAYMENT_PAID` ↔ `PAYMENT_SUCCESS` trong handler registry.
- Internal ingest dùng cho dev/test khi Kafka chưa có; production ưu tiên `FR_ConsumeDomainEvent`.

